instructions: To go to the Home screen, swipe up from the bottom edge of the screen (on an iPhone with Face ID) or press the Home button (on other iPhone models). Swipe left or right to browse apps on other Home screen pages. To open an app, tap its icon on the Home screen. To return to the first Home screen page, swipe up from the bottom edge of the screen (on an iPhone with Face ID) or press the Home button (on other iPhone models).
